{"tid":262272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"19歲女與父亂倫發展畸戀 稱因妒忌父親再婚","createTime":"2017-05-29T05:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T06:45:36.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"664478b3523e66656ad3fafc4e5bebf4c19b3764","tid":262272,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"8年前19歲的少女在安慰心情低落的中醫父親(當時51歲)時，卻跟他亂倫性交，獻出自己初夜，兩人關係更一直持續並拍下性交片段。父女早前在區院承認兩項亂倫罪，女兒一方今求情指，自母親離家出走後她女兼母職，並錯將愛情投放在父親身上，因得知父親打算與未婚妻再婚，感到妒忌想到獻身父親以作挽留。<br />\n<br />\n現年26歲的女被告，其大狀求情指本案不涉違反誠信，且十分不尋常，案中女兒與父親並未如一般案件視對方為性伴侶，又指女兒為了父親，曾想過自己攬罪以換取父親可脫身。<br />\n<br />\n大狀又稱，女被告胞弟當日舉報案件純因愛護胞姐希望保講她，並不知胞姊其實出於自願，事後受大打擊並患上抑鬱，需服藥治療，胞弟寫信向姊透露「你是我生命一部分」，不能想像沒有胞姊的生活如何渡過。大狀指女被告對其他人的傷害性低，對她而言，接受輔導更有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n至於父親的代表大狀則求情指，被告對所做的事感後悔和知錯，明白所做的事有違倫理，會負法律責任，又稱得到家人支持，報告指他重犯機會低，案發時女兒已是成年人且出於自願，他並無使用武力，要求輕判。<br />\n<br />\n法官考慮到報告指被女被告需要心理輔導，故接納大狀要求再索取感化官報告，押後案件至下月12日始將兩父女一同判刑。<br />\n<br />\n被告父親現年59歲，於2013年離婚、女兒則現年26歲，他們透露首次亂倫發生在2009至2011年間，第二次於2015年10月至11月間。"},{"pid":"10df8005114735f34e15b08b513d2daafe76feb3","tid":262272,"uid":107279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:56:57.000Z","msg":"ON9胞弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c811306caad495e0dd07c68fc33a27ac0d2fa0","tid":262272,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"細路無得玩咪報警囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79229ed8c11cf65c9b3a7b3c769dcdf5ef66d81","tid":262272,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"自己冇份玩走去玩踢爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f66eac99c0aa79638a18ee3469e72fe40416713","tid":262272,"uid":49853,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"細佬鍾意左家姐，家姐鍾意左老豆，老豆鍾意左第二個女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c540e2644f16af9c8ae1767b4fa1c5abe948bb","tid":262272,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:00:40.000Z","msg":"無罪啦"},{"pid":"3a66c5a53cb03fe68ee606e143ba0377720c1aa2","tid":262272,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細佬鍾意左家姐，家姐鍾意左老豆，老豆鍾意左第二個女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b353cd65ce4ddd2082c4fb38e1cc519fab408b3e","tid":262272,"uid":60814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細佬鍾意左家姐，家姐鍾意左老豆，老豆鍾意左第二個女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntvb新劇情節"},{"pid":"43af7446b7385106783de7d111d1e727b94959fa","tid":262272,"uid":41076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:02:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細佬鍾意左家姐，家姐鍾意左老豆，老豆鍾意左第二個女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個女人鍾意返細佬<br />\n4p happy end <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195768f02c2c6bb5cf238c108364d40f12ff0c71","tid":262272,"uid":98692,"like